<div id="app">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24 lg:py-12">
    <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-bloom-brass">Bloom Club Checkout</p>
    <h1 class="font-serif-tc mt-4 text-[34px] font-bold leading-[46px] text-bloom-ink md:text-[44px] md:leading-[64px]">結帳</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 max-w-[620px] text-base leading-[23px] text-bloom-muted">
      填寫收件資訊並確認花禮明細，送出後將前往綠界付款。
    </p>

    <div v-if="loading" class="flex justify-center py-16">
      <div class="h-8 w-8 animate-spin rounded-full border-4 border-bloom-brass border-t-transparent"></div>
    </div>

    <div v-else class="mt-12 grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_minmax(320px,440px)]">
      <div class="min-w-0 rounded-lg border border-bloom-line bg-bloom-ivory p-5 shadow-[0_18px_34px_rgba(13,33,28,0.08),0_4px_8px_rgba(13,33,28,0.04)] md:p-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 border-b border-bloom-line pb-6">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-bloom-brass">Recipient</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif-tc text-[26px] font-semibold leading-9 text-bloom-green">收件資訊</h2>
          <p class="text-[13px] leading-5 text-bloom-muted">請填寫花禮配送資訊，Email 將用於付款與訂單通知。</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-7 space-y-5">
          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-bloom-muted">收件人姓名</label>
            <input
              v-model="form.recipientName"
              type="text"
              placeholder="請輸入收件人姓名"
              class="mt-2 h-12 w-full rounded-lg border border-bloom-line bg-bloom-cream px-4 text-sm text-bloom-ink transition-colors placeholder:text-bloom-muted/70 focus:border-bloom-brass focus:outline-none"
            />
            <p v-if="errors.recipientName" class="mt-2 text-xs text-red-600">{{ errors.recipientName }}</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-bloom-muted">Email</label>
            <input
              v-model="form.recipientEmail"
              type="email"
              placeholder="請輸入 Email"
              class="mt-2 h-12 w-full rounded-lg border border-bloom-line bg-bloom-cream px-4 text-sm text-bloom-ink transition-colors placeholder:text-bloom-muted/70 focus:border-bloom-brass focus:outline-none"
            />
            <p v-if="errors.recipientEmail" class="mt-2 text-xs text-red-600">{{ errors.recipientEmail }}</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-bloom-muted">收件地址</label>
            <input
              v-model="form.recipientAddress"
              type="text"
              placeholder="請輸入收件地址"
              class="mt-2 h-12 w-full rounded-lg border border-bloom-line bg-bloom-cream px-4 text-sm text-bloom-ink transition-colors placeholder:text-bloom-muted/70 focus:border-bloom-brass focus:outline-none"
            />
            <p v-if="errors.recipientAddress" class="mt-2 text-xs text-red-600">{{ errors.recipientAddress }}</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 rounded-lg border border-bloom-line bg-bloom-cream px-5 py-4">
          <h3 class="font-serif-tc text-base font-semibold text-bloom-ink">付款提醒</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-bloom-muted">
            送出訂單後會建立待付款訂單，並自動導向綠界付款頁。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="min-w-0 rounded-lg bg-bloom-green p-6 text-bloom-ivory shadow-[0_18px_34px_rgba(13,33,28,0.10),0_4px_8px_rgba(13,33,28,0.04)] md:p-9 lg:sticky lg:top-32 lg:h-fit">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-bloom-brass">Order Summary</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif-tc mt-3 text-[28px] font-bold leading-[41px]">訂單摘要</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-[13px] leading-[19px] text-bloom-sage">
          確認商品金額後，下一步前往綠界付款。
        </p>

        <div class="mt-7 h-px bg-bloom-sage/70"></div>

        <div class="mt-7 space-y-5">
          <div
            v-for="item in cartItems"
            :key="item.id"
            class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 text-sm"
          >
            <div class="min-w-0">
              <p class="truncate text-bloom-ivory">{{ item.product.name }}</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-bloom-sage">數量 {{ item.quantity }}</p>
            </div>
            <span class="shrink-0 font-medium text-bloom-ivory">
              NT$ {{ (item.product.price * item.quantity).toLocaleString() }}
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 h-px bg-bloom-sage/70"></div>

        <div class="mt-7 flex flex-col gap-2 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
          <span class="text-lg font-bold">總計</span>
          <span class="font-serif-tc text-[28px] font-bold leading-[41px] text-bloom-brass">
            NT$ {{ cartTotal.toLocaleString() }}
          </span>
        </div>

        <button
          @click="submitOrder"
          :disabled="submitting"
          class="mt-8 h-14 w-full rounded-lg bg-bloom-brass text-[13px] font-semibold text-bloom-deep transition-colors hover:bg-[#D4B777] disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:opacity-50"
        >
          {{ submitting ? '處理中...' : '前往綠界付款' }}
        </button>

        <a
          href="/cart"
          class="mt-4 flex h-11 w-full items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-bloom-line text-[13px] font-semibold text-bloom-ivory transition-colors hover:text-bloom-brass"
        >
          返回購物車
        </a>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
